videos.description: De'Aaron Fox's intended lob to Marvin Bagley III doesn't work out, but the ball bounces off the glass to Buddy Hield, who scores a bucket for the Kings.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Fox gets an unintentional assist off the glass) 2021/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fox gets an unintentional assist off the glass

videos.description: Harrison Barnes shakes and bakes as he works his way through the paint on a pair of contested baskets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Barnes shows off his skills on back-to-back makes) 2021/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Barnes shows off his skills on back-to-back makes

videos.description: LaMelo Ball splits the defenders and throws up the falling baby hook while drawing the foul.

videos.headline: LaMelo takes a fall while scoring the and-1 bucket

videos.description: De'Aaron Fox dribbles behind the back, tripping up the defender before draining the jump shot.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Fox skillfully scores the fadeaway jumper) 2021/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fox skillfully scores the fadeaway jumper

videos.description: Malik Monk drives through the paint and slams it down with authority as the Hornets inch closer to the Kings' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Monk hyped after massive dunk) 2021/03/15 ESHEET

videos.headline: Monk hyped after massive dunk

videos.description: Gordon Hayward tips the pass for a steal then hustles back and takes a swing on the basket after the go-ahead dunk.

videos.headline: Hornets bench ignites as Hayward slams it down

videos.description: Nemanja Bjelica throws up a quick off-balance jumper and it beats the buzzer to end the third quarter.
videos.headline: Bjelica drains the buzzer-beater

videos.description: Richaun Holmes refuses to allow Bismack Biyombo to score the easy bucket.

videos.headline: Holmes aggressively denies Biyombo at the rim
